{
  "stem": "25598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it really was spring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So every season had-- and that sort of added to the fact that you knew what to expect, And you knew how it's going to be tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then suddenly, you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Pesach was a really big deal, a really big deal because we had an attic in the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our house consisted of four apartments, which my paternal grandparents built because they had three children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they built an apartment for each of the children and one for themselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It didn't turn out that way, but that's what happened when they built the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so the third floor of the house was an attic where we kept the Pesach dishes, and all kinds of seasonal things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So getting the dishes down from the attic, and washing them and shining them and this was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it took about a week or two to clean the house from chametz and get all the-- the tablecloth were different for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was-- the-- the candlesticks were different for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was different.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the house, of course, was always-- my mother was compulsively clean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything had to shine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a lot of crystal in the house, and a lot of Chinese porcelains and stuff.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything was shining, and everything was sparkling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- the smells of the food, and the-- it was just-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was-- it's very moving to me, to remember those times because I've never had them again.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
